message: #9425 We were together. Alone. I had the chance to say what we were both thinking, but I didn't. Now that the opportunity's passed, you don't look at me the same way. I'm sorry.  I still think you're amazing, and only wish you thought the same.

#9424 I rode my bicycle to the bottle store yesterday and bought bottle of brandy.  I was about to leave when I realized that if I fell off my bike on the way home, the bottle would break.  So I drank all the brandy before I rode back, which was a good thing, because I fell off my bike seven times on the way home
